This paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes a new method for policy optimization in reinforcement learning. It may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category as it deals with improving the efficiency of RL algorithms. The paper's focus on continuous control tasks suggests it may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Additionally, the use of pathwise consistencies may suggest a systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category. Finally, the evaluation of the proposed method on control tasks may suggest a computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category.
